{"tid":231884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"又到馬會派錢既時候","createTime":"2017-05-06T11:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T12:13:58.000Z","uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16a92b24b3a949d6f07ce7974bb8e1a3c9973eda","tid":231884,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3txxdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3txxdd.jpg&h=ccac2d73&s={SIZE}\" />[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3bf24a5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/190835_ef45ea1873845e432d534d07fac3d26f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F190835_ef45ea1873845e432d534d07fac3d26f.jpg&h=ff2552b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/190836_47e9509cccecddb8932cd2b2e566b84e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F190836_47e9509cccecddb8932cd2b2e566b84e.jpg&h=0a338519&s={SIZE}\" />/190834_ef45ea1873845e432d534d07fac3d26f.jpg[/img]<br />\n<br />\n又到馬會派錢既時候<br />\n重注買車仔冠軍當收息都好<br />\n<br />\n可能有人覺得3%唔係派錢<br />\n但睇你買幾多<br />\n1萬已有3百<br />\n如你本多派既錢仲多<br />\n真係同派股息差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢D機會一年唔係成日有<br />\n錯過就冇<br />\n馬會講真今日都已可封盤<br />\n唔封盤可能只係為引D熱刺球迷買熱刺"},{"pid":"3788e137501de41e7df3da628945990307bc5a49","tid":231884,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:13:34.000Z","msg":"5月28日或之前已知結果<br />\n仲快過等收股息"},{"pid":"5c1e59ac6a79f16c567de40bca3778b81ee9e3a4","tid":231884,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:17:42.000Z","msg":"真係同派錢冇分別，不過冇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15417815a4be53c46b2b9c6a796ddf6da2447ad","tid":231884,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係同派錢冇分別，不過冇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平時儲下錢<br />\n就係可以咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8a91a8580e336e56e6c3613625286c5470ca99","tid":231884,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"仲有曼聯客勝3.8"},{"pid":"ad21c0355a2b277ea7293c61bf7033dc774b210b","tid":231884,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"你會唔會攞十皮搏三千先"},{"pid":"6aa995d51e277283bdb21e59e73d6bfd82966e66","tid":231884,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"表面上係3厘<br />\n但年利率係護計1年<br />\n依家1個月內就3厘<br />\n計年利率即係2X%<br />\n呢D機會係香港<br />\n只有馬會先會去開善堂<br />\n李嘉誠都唔會比呢D機會你"},{"pid":"d2de65525632083e187d00b6c19374bcd99170ae","tid":231884,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"你要赴南極　我話曼城<br />\n人人有份舉手　投一份"},{"pid":"c90ecef1bf49e9245bfbb5e2662d86f82f6e2982","tid":231884,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你會唔會攞十皮搏三千先</blockquote><br />\n對於今日仲質疑熱刺會贏冠軍既人<br />\n我相信佢唔熟英超或足球<br />\n或者無留意餘下賽程<br />\n<br />\n就算主客和1.2倍我都會重注買<br />\n今次係99.99999999.......%贏梗<br />\n要車仔輸冠軍<br />\n除非成隊交通意外或受恐佈襲擊有傷亡啦<br />\n<br />\n你如果覺得係廢話就自動skip<br />\n到時月尾派錢馬會唔預你"},{"pid":"320be8b353b60cd842f6b605ef9803e49882ce07","tid":231884,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你會唔會攞十皮搏三千先</blockquote><br />\n對於今日仲質疑熱刺會贏冠軍既人<br />\